{"tid":1473194,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「團結」我地5年前輸左 今次仲點可以再輸","createTime":"2019-08-14T18:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T02:38:48.000Z","uid":36716,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"262439ba06a582d3736f606d8dbc7182092feaa5","tid":1473194,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUxS36O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUxS36O.jpg&h=c1e06733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五年前,我們輸了,一敗涂地。我哋失去朋友，失去家人，失去部分的自我。如今我們有機會<br />\n扭轉乾坤，你哋知道自己的團隊和任務，討回自由，救他們回來！<br />\n<br />\n我想同年輕一輩講，對唔住。5年前因為我地輸左而令你地今個暑假咁辛苦<br />\n<br />\n希望有朝一日，我哋可以除低眼罩口罩係立法會慶祝同相認"},{"pid":"d8a399a0ba5c4abe4e3fc394e91fe038708cda4b","tid":1473194,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:57:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c870efdcdd56b9b553499b33affaddf4399c3f8b","tid":1473194,"uid":241865,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:15:41.000Z","msg":"我都唔想輸<br />\n一輸左，後果比雨運更加慘烈...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83bbc8c7b9b65f8318c4daf9eb79165a8d93ee9","tid":1473194,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:34:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">818， 追討黑警濫權!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818， 正視警黑合作!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXPug1n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXPug1n.jpg&h=448ec9ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"beacdf39bb65c26fbbad4030127e96fec2eedfbe","tid":1473194,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:36:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dac170cb3b18b791af0da56f968d5a320959372","tid":1473194,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0